# Ran on CLI for X-Ray Sampling
# CLI: aws xray create-group \ --group-name "Cruddur" --filter-expression "service(\"backend-flask\")"

#Create sampling for x-ray
# CLI: aws xray create-sampling-rule --cli-input-json file://aws/json/xray.json
# On Cloudwatch create sample by ---> CloudWatch --> Settings --> X-Ray traces --> Sampling rules (View settings) --> Create sampling rule